<h4>
        BigBrother and MRTG<!-- #$loop:item['xar_title']# -->
               </h4>
<!-- show changelog -->
<!-- end changelog -->
           <span class="xar-sub">
Posted by:                     Anonymous Coward
 on                 November 02, 2005 05:02 PM</span>
       </div>
       <div class="xar-accent xar-cm-comment">

                 
            
              Big Brother: &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.bb4.org/&quot; title=&quot;bb4.org&quot;&gt;http://www.bb4.org/&lt;/a bb4.org&gt;<br>monitors all your servers and services, disk space etc. It displays all the info on an easy to read webpage, and can be configured to send alerts when the warning levels are reached e.g. hard disk reaches 90% etc.<br><br>And MRTG of course&lt;nobr&gt; &lt;wbr&gt;&lt;/nobr&gt;:)<br><br>Both of these also provide records of how well your system have been running.....providing thats a good thing to know&lt;nobr&gt; &lt;wbr&gt;&lt;/nobr&gt;:) 

                <p>
                    <a href="http://www.linux.com/archive/?module=comments&amp;func=display&amp;cid=1149241" title="Permalink" rel="bookmark">
                       #
                   </a>
               </p>

